00:15:13.790 --> 00:15:15.820
PAUL BAKAUS: Well I just wanted
to say, one big issue,

00:15:15.820 --> 00:15:17.505
I think, with rendering
performance and measuring

00:15:17.505 --> 00:15:20.140
