it's harder to isolate

00:15:20.140 --> 00:15:21.640
it on the actual device--

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:24.660
because it might be entirely
the user fault why

00:15:24.660 --> 00:15:26.070
rendering is down.

00:15:26.070 --> 00:15:29.200
