00:18:09.420 --> 00:18:12.530
When we talk about your
performance drops, your

00:18:12.530 --> 00:18:15.830
conversion drops, your
engagement drops, we have good

00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:17.020
measurements--

00:18:17.020 --> 00:18:19.590
