Would you like to come up and
ask it regarding Chrome

00:30:11.000 --> 00:30:13.818
performance versus--

00:30:13.818 --> 00:30:15.530
ANDRE: Sure.

00:30:15.530 --> 00:30:16.660
JAMES PEARCE: You're
on record.

00:30:16.660 --> 00:30:17.562
[LAUGHTER]

00:30:17.562 --> 00:30:18.812
ANDRE: Great.

