On the iPad, it's
really great.

00:31:16.420 --> 00:31:20.130
On most Android devices,
it's pretty good.

00:31:20.130 --> 00:31:23.400
And I'm wondering what
the difference is?

00:31:23.400 --> 00:31:29.010
TOM WILTZIUS: Yeah, so some of
