Greg, you want to
say something?

00:35:47.150 --> 00:35:48.550
GREG SIMON: Yeah.

00:35:48.550 --> 00:35:50.070
TOM WILTZIUS: Burns all
your CPU, which

00:35:50.070 --> 00:35:50.870
burns all your power.

